title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-16-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-16-2013 
















The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET


Glenn and crew covering breaking news of a shooting at a DC naval yard.
 Stay tuned though out the day for updates on this situation.

 Also on the show Glenn takes on Bill Nye as he mocks religion.

 We also have updates on the Syria situation that have been developing during the weekend.
